      "text": "Jo tu eſſi man par Patwerumu/ weens ſtirps Turnis\nprett manneem Eenaidneefeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es palifſchu eeſch tawa Dſhwofka muſchigi/es patwerschohs appakich tawu Spahrnu Paſlehpuunu/ Sela.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tu Deews eſſi mannas Apfohlifchanas klautijs/ tu ce.dohdi weenu Behrnu Mantutem/ kaſ tawu Wahrdru bihſtahe.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu wairotti tam Kehnimam to Dſhwibas Laiku/winna Gadoi paliks lihds Raddu Raddeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiſch paſehdehs muſchigi Deewa Preeſchâ/ parahti winnam Schehlaſtibu un Bateeſibu/ kaſ winnu paſarga.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad Dſeedatchu es tawam Wahrdam muſchigi/ ka es fa.was Apfohlifchanas maſtaju iſdeenas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta LXII. Dſeesma.\nIer weena Eepreezinaschanaſ Dſeesma/ eeſch ka Dahwids tahs Deewa Palihdsibas eeprec.yinajahs: 2. Un tapehz ſaweem Eenaidneefeem ſmeijahs: 5. Pamahza arridſan wiſſus/kaſ Lifſâ un Behdâs irraid/ ka tee ueDeewa Palihdsibu ween pataujahs: 9. Iq Zilweku Palihdsiba teeti ne derr: 10. etc.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Eena Dahwida Dſeesma/ preeſch ta angſtaDſeedataja zaar Jedutun.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tatschu manna Dwchfeleirr kluffu pee Deewa/no winna nahe umana Peſtischana.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tatschu wiſch irr mAkminâ Kalns un manna ſtischana/ mans Patwerumses tik gauschi ne ſchaubischohs\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Zik ilgi juhs Launnudohmajat prett weenn Wihiuhs tapſeet wiſſi nokauti/ jubuſſeet ka weena celihkuſi Sna/ un dauihts Muhris.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tee ween Padohmu twinnu no ſawas Godibasgabſt/ teem patihk Melli/ arwu Mutti winni ſwehti/ Sirđs Dibbinâ winni lahSela.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tatschu manna Dwchfezeeti Deewam kluſſu/ jo no winna irr manna Zerriba.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiſch weenuuſehr tmans Akmina Kalns un manPeſtischana/ mans Patwerumika es ne ſchaubischohs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pee Deewa irr manna Pſtischana/ un mans Godemanma Stipruma Akminsmanna Gelbetchana ſtahw uDeewu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Zerrejeet us winnu allschin juhs Lauttri/ iſgahſeet fwu Sirđi winna PreeſchâDeewu irr mumu par Patwerimu/ Sela.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tatschu Zilweku Behrleeti ne derr/ leelem Landim iarriſfan Wainas/ kad tee Swaru Kaufâ taptu uſwiltti/ tabuhtu tee kehpa (weeglati/) ka patti Neleeſiba.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ne pataujeetes us Netaifnibu un Laupifchannu/ ne to\n"
    }
